  "detailed_description": "<h1>🎉 Steam Trading Cards Are Here for Gun Crazy! 🔫✨</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hey everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’re excited to announce that <strong>Gun Crazy</strong> now features <strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong>! Whether you’re blasting through levels with pixel-perfect precision or just jumping in for a quick arcade fix, you can now collect and unlock awesome new goodies while doing it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here’s what you can look forward to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>Trading Cards</strong> to collect and swap</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>Badges</strong> to craft and show off your arcade cred</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖼️ <strong>Backgrounds</strong> to customize your Steam profile</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😺 <strong>Emoticons</strong> inspired by the action-packed mayhem of Gun Crazy</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks as always for your support, and stay crazy out there! 💥</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897640/extras/e5cdc6f615a91ad903097044c48a1727.poster.avif?t=1772895149\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897640/extras/e5cdc6f615a91ad903097044c48a1727.webm?t=1772895149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897640/extras/e5cdc6f615a91ad903097044c48a1727.mp4?t=1772895149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gun Crazy</strong> is a fast paced and hectic arcade style action shoot em’ up, sporting old school pixel art and a retro sound track.<br><br>Tackle <strong>bosses</strong>, dodge an onslaught of bullets, and use <strong>multiple weapons</strong> to take out your foes. Hope you brought 